high_descs: turn right, walk to the white table on the left
grab the knife on the table
turn right, walk to the sink on the left
put the knife in the sink, wash the knife, take the knife out
turn around, walk to the white table
put the knife down on the white table by the wine bottle
anns.task_desc: wash the knife from the white table, put it back on the white table

high_descs: turn right, and advance to just before the stove. Stop, turn left, and advance to the table, stopping in front of the knife on the left-hand side of the table
take the knife from the table
turn around and cross the room to the sink
place the knife in the right-hand sink, rinse the knife, and pick the knife back up
turn around and return to in front of the rectangular table
place the knife to the right of the wine bottle
anns.task_desc: Place a wet knife on the table

high_descs: turn right and walk past the fridge on your right, then turn left and walk over to the white table at the end of the room
grab a butter knife off of the table there
move over to the sink on the right side of the room at the end of the room
place the knife inside the sink and clean it off, then take it back out again
turn around and head over to the kitchen table on the right side of the room
place the knife down on the kitchen table
anns.task_desc: place a clean knife on the kitchen table

high_descs: Walk forward to the table with the football on it.
Pick up the knife to the left of the bottle on the table.
Turn right and walk to the sink on the right.
Rinse the knife in the sink on the right and then pick up the knife from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the table with the football on it.
Place the knife to the right of the bottle on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean knife on the table with the football on it.
